<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10130514>
    dc:description "FIG. 29. — Diploexochus exu Campos-Filho, Sfenthourakis & Bichuette, n. sp., female paratype LES 28003: A, uropod, frontal view; B, uropod; C, pereopod 1; D, pereopod 7; E, pleopod 2 exopod; F, pleopod 3 exopod; G, pleopod 4 exopod; H, pleopod 5 exopod." ;
